9
00:00:47,073 --> 00:00:50,744
Moss matrix, gentle engine, keep me kind.

10
00:00:50,744 --> 00:00:53,697
Slow algorithm, hold the line.

11
00:00:53,697 --> 00:00:56,170
No fast-forward on this hillside spine,

12
