13
00:01:09,254 --> 00:01:11,808
Talk of a cheatcode, thumb-tap fate,

14
00:01:11,808 --> 00:01:14,600
reload a save from a cleaner slate.

15
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:17,552
Konami craving in a tender ache,

16
00:01:17,552 --> 00:01:20,027
