17
00:01:20,027 --> 00:01:23,058
But snapshots blur when the rain sets in,

18
00:01:23,058 --> 00:01:25,611
checkpoints smear, we start again.

19
00:01:25,611 --> 00:01:28,644
Eventual consistency under the pine,

20
00:01:28,644 --> 00:01:30,447
two careful hands, one steady time.

21
00:01:30,798 --> 00:01:35,027
Moss matrix, patient teacher, set the pace.

22
00:01:35,027 --> 00:01:38,697
Slow convergence, softer trace.

23
00:01:38,697 --> 00:01:41,090
Rollback dreams fade out of place,

24
00:01:41,090 --> 00:02:04,278
commit to breath, commit to grace.

25
00:02:04,628 --> 00:02:08,456
Anneal in the cold, then warm by noon,

26
00:02:08,456 --> 00:02:10,770
energy landscape hums a tune.

27
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:13,723
Gradient descent on a grief-shaped hill,

28
00:02:13,723 --> 00:02:16,754
