33
00:02:27,686 --> 00:02:30,717
I test my pulse on a ring of rings,

34
00:02:30,717 --> 00:02:33,032
age in the trunk where the winter sings.

35
00:02:33,032 --> 00:02:36,383
Asymptote love, never quite done,

36
