37
00:02:39,414 --> 00:02:42,605
Moss matrix, long renderer of light.

38
00:02:42,605 --> 00:02:44,919
Scene compiles through day to night.

39
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:47,793
Patience wins when pixels are bright,

40
00:02:47,793 --> 00:03:13,532
green little proofs that we got it right.

41
00:03:13,883 --> 00:03:16,754
Quantum of comfort, dew bead, dawn,

42
00:03:16,754 --> 00:03:19,467
decohere sorrow till edges are gone.

43
00:03:19,467 --> 00:03:22,580
Planck-small promises, tiny and true,

44
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:25,133
