49
00:03:37,100 --> 00:03:40,372
Moss matrix, coder of the ground.

50
00:03:40,372 --> 00:03:43,245
Low frequency mercy, round and round.

51
00:03:43,245 --> 00:03:45,956
No secret code to skip the wound,

52
00:03:45,956 --> 00:03:54,145
